- **Block Explorer:** [View Blocks](http://xai-api-lb-835033547.us-east-1.elb.amazonaws.com/explorer)
- **Faucet:** [Get Test Tokens](http://xai-api-lb-835033547.us-east-1.elb.amazonaws.com/faucet)

